2; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">从事烟草制品零售业务的个人必须是年满<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>周岁以上具有完全民事行为能力的人。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第七条</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">从事烟草制品零售业务的公民、法人或者其他组织申请办理烟草专卖零售许可证应当提交如下申请材料：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（一）申请书原件一份；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（二）守法经营承诺书原件一份；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（三）经营场所证明材料（自有产权证或者租赁合同）复印件一份，租赁合同必须加盖印章；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（四）经营者有效身份证复印件或者法定代表人任命文件原件和复印件以及有效身份证复印件一份。法定代表人任命文件原件和复印件是针对集体证而言；（注释：核查无误后，原件返还申请人，复印件存档。）</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（五）经营者或者法定代表人近期一寸免冠彩色登记照两张；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（六）经营烟草制品零售业务有效资金证明一份（资金证明的书面材料，包括申请人的银行存折复印件、可以证明存款额度的银行卡复印件）。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第八条 </span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">零售点合理布局的具体标准：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-layout-grid-align: none\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（一）</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">城市繁华区，人口密集、人流量大的主要干道两旁，零售点的设置同侧间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"20\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>，异侧间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"10\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"> <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-layout-grid-align: none\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（二）城市中心区，人流量较大的主要干道两旁，零售点的设置同侧间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"30\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>，异侧间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"20\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-layout-grid-align: none\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（三）城区一般路段，人流量较小的街道两旁，零售点的设置同侧间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"50\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>，异侧间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"30\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（四）乡镇政府驻地主要街道零售点的设置其间隔不少于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"20\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；乡镇沿线公路零售点的设置其间距不小于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"200\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；农村行政村零售点的设置，人口密集的村组根据实际情况适当增设零售点，但毗邻两户之间间隔不小于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"100\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>；边远农村、山区等自然村可按每<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>户设置<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>个零售点；</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"> <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（五）集贸市场、各类综合（批发）市场等场所零售店的设置，原则上不超过商户总数的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5%</span>，零售点之间保持适当的距离；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（六）各类住宅小区、社区类，按每<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">150</span>户设立<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>个零售店的原则设置，但<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"200\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>范围内不得超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>个零售点；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（七）车站、码头零售点按占地面积和人流量的大小适当设置；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（八）大型企事业单位等内部场所，可按每<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>人设立一个零售点的原则设置，毗邻两户零售点之间间隔不小于<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"20\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第九条 <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">属于下列情形，按照一点一证的原则办理，并且不作为其它零售点合理布局的参照项，不受距离间隔的控制。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">酒店、餐馆、度假村、娱乐场所、体育场馆、茶室等相对封闭、以满足停留在设施内特定顾客消费的经营场所；大中型超市、购物中心以及连锁经营的商业企业；国道、省道上的服务区和加油站内设置的便利店；但与卷烟有关的招牌、商标、柜台等不准向临街面摆放。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十条</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">有下列情形之一的，不得设立零售点：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（一） 经营化工、油漆、药品、农药、化肥、建材、装潢等易燃易爆、易挥发、有毒、有害商品以及基于其他安全因素不适宜经营烟草制品零售业务的，不得设立零售点。法律、法规、规章和行业管理规划中允许设立零售点的除外；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（二）无固定经营场所的。包括：电话亭、美容（理发）亭、书（报）亭、冰柜、自动售货柜、临时流动摊位、临时搭建的简易房；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（三）利用自动售货机、通过信息网络销售卷烟的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（四）幼儿园、小学、中学校园内（教职工生活区除外）及门口<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"50\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>范围内（偏远山区、农村地区<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"50\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>范围内）；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（五）租房合同有效期限不满一年的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（六）</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">违章建筑、临时建筑或规划半年内待拆迁的建筑物；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（七）居住场所和经营场所无法分离的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（八）外商投资的商业企业或个体工商户，或者以特许、吸纳加盟店及其他再投资等形式变相从事烟草制品经营业务的；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（九）取消从事烟草专卖业务资格不满三年的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（十）因申请人隐瞒有关情况或者提供虚假材料，烟草部门作出不予受理或者不予发证决定后，申请人在一年内再次提出申请的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（十一）因申请人以欺骗、贿赂等不正当手段取得的烟草专卖许可证被撤销后，申请人三年内再次提出申请的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（十二）未领取烟草专卖零售许可证经营烟草专卖品业务，并且一年内被执法机关处罚两次以上，在三年内申请领取烟草专卖零售许可证的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">（十三）</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">申请人注册的名称中含有&ldquo;卷烟批发、名优卷烟批发、名烟专卖&rdquo;等字样的；在店面招牌和经营场所中未经批准擅自使用&ldquo;中国烟草&rdquo;标识的，未经授权擅自使用卷烟生产厂家卷烟商品商标标识的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（十四）</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">法律、法规、规章规定不宜设置零售点的其它场所。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十一条<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">对社会弱势群体（残疾人、特困户、军烈属及下岗职工），符合相关规定的，持有效证明，经核实后可适当放宽准入条件办理。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十二条<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在同一地段，同时存在两个或两个以上申请人的，按申请受理时间的先后顺序做出许可决定。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">第三章<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span>特别规定<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十三条</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">有下列情形之一的，应当取消所设置的零售点，已发放的烟草专卖零售许可证依照有关法律规定同时收回：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（一）烟草专卖零售许可证有效期届满未办理延续申请的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（二）烟草专卖零售许可证核定的经营主体为自然人，自然人死亡或丧失民事行为能力的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（三）烟草专卖零售许可证核定的经营主体为法人或其他组织依法终止的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（四）登记事项发生改变后，持证人未按照规划提出变更申请，自收到责令变更许可证通知书<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日内仍拒绝变更的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（五）停止经营业务<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>年以上不办理停业手续，或办理了停业手续、停业期届满后未申请恢复营业的，经发证机关公告<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>个月后仍未申请歇业或申请恢复营业的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（六）已取得烟草专卖零售许可证的企业或个人（除农村户或工商行政主管部门明文规定可以不办理工商营业执照情况外），自收到许可证之日起六个月内不办理工商营业执照开展经营活动的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（七）烟草专卖零售许可证被依法撤销的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（八）烟草专卖零售许可证被依法撤回的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（九）烟草专卖零售许可证被依法取消从事烟草专卖零售业务资格的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（十）烟草专卖零售许可证持证人被工商行政主管部门吊销、注销营业执照的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（十一）擅自改变经营场所出入口、经营面积或其它申请登记事项，并导致原作出许可条件发生改变的；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（十二）已取得烟草专卖零售许可证的加油站便利店，每年必须通过消防部门年检或抽检，如达不到安全方面相关规划的或没有年审合格证的，将不予延续有效期或者直接取消从事烟草专卖零售业务的资格；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（十三）法律、法规、规章规划的其他情形。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十四条</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">本规定实施前批准设立的零售点不符合本规定的，通过市场调节和依法监督管理逐步达到本规定的设置标准。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十五条</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">在本规定实施前已取得烟草专卖零售许可证的，许可期满后申请延续或因经营者、经营地址变更等需要重新申请许可的，按照本规定执行。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">第四章<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span>附 则</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十六条</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">本规定所称城市繁华区是指：凤凰大道、沙阳大道、鱼岳大道。中心区是指：发展大道、人民大道、迎宾大道、沿湖大道、樱花大道。一般区是指：西正街、东岳路、通湖路、龙潭大道、岳公路、北门二路、北街、滨湖路、戴湾路、茶庵路、女婿街、东街、环城路、考棚村、磨盘路、南湖路、南街、麒麟路、球场小区、吴梅何路、小新堤路、烟墩路。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十七条<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">本规定所称零售点间隔距离是指两个零售点间的可通行距离，也可称行进距离。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">本规定中的&ldquo;同侧&rdquo;指两个零售点之间的最近行走路线不需跨越道路的情况，&ldquo;异侧&rdquo;指两个零售点之间的最近行走路线需跨越道路的情况（异侧距离包含道路宽度）。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">间隔测量时以两个零售点之间的最近距离测量。测量时申请人和烟草专卖管理人员必须同时在场，并书面认可。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十八条<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">本规定所称参照项是指已取得烟草专卖零售许可证，具有合法经营烟草制品零售业务资格的零售点。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第十九条</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">本规定中关于经营场所的界定是指：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（一）申请人堆放货物的储藏室、仓库与经营门店相分离的，视为经营场所的附属仓库，有义务接受烟草专卖管理部门的监督检查；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（二）&ldquo;与住所相对独立的固定经营场所&rdquo;是指经营场所不应为住所或住所的一部分，应为非住宅性质的固定经营场所；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（三）房屋权属证明材料中标明房屋性质为&ldquo;商铺&rdquo;的房屋，因日常经营需临时居住的，申请人在提交办证申请时需申明临时居住场所为固定经营场所的一部分，并自愿接受专卖执法人员的执法检查；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">（四）&ldquo;经营场所是否与住所相对独立&rdquo;，需经专卖执法人员实地勘测画图后确定；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30.1pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">第二十条<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">本规定由嘉鱼县烟草专卖局负责解释，自公告之日起施行。嘉鱼县烟草专卖局<st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"28\\\\\" month=\\\\\"3\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2008\\\\\">二八年三月二十八日</st1:chsdate>制定的《嘉鱼县烟草制品零售点合理布局规定》同时废止。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 30pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 292.5pt; margin: 14.3pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 19.5\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 15pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-in